    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147050/extras/38993183beeaca967ac381061bf60f11.avif?t=1723346766\" width=624 height=390 /></span><br>可爱风格的跳跃冒险游戏——猫岛物语” 是一款简单直白的平台跳跃游戏，为了复活失落的王国，猫猫英雄穿上披风，克服重重困难在充满陷阱的地下城中收集金币与猫爪宝石！齿轮、荆棘、暗器、火焰、岩浆弹等不同的陷阱正在地下城中正静候冒失的入侵者，但是不要畏惧我勇敢的小猫，利用猫猫特有的能力攀墙而上吧，宝石就在那里等你！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏特色：</strong></h2><br>游戏操作简单，质朴的跳跃和移动带你轻松上手，灵活运用弹墙跳和墙面滑动来巧妙地化解地城中的陷阱。不过不要放心的太早，被躲过的陷阱也许也会突然追击而至！从每一次失败中汲取教训，勇敢猫猫无所畏惧！挑战万难夺得宝石。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏内容：</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147050/extras/530e887a9cc506466b31d4f166180b1f.poster.avif?t=1723346766\" width=202 height=152 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147050/extras/530e887a9cc506466b31d4f166180b1f.webm?t=1723346766\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147050/extras/530e887a9cc506466b31d4f166180b1f.mp4?t=1723346766\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147050/extras/328d1861d06a000e6ffa1e650741c320.poster.avif?t=1723346766\" width=202 height=152 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147050/extras/328d1861d06a000e6ffa1e650741c320.webm?t=1723346766\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147050/extras/328d1861d06a000e6ffa1e650741c320.mp4?t=1723346766\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147050/extras/4913fa74f6d0ba820e152dc073ba6ce0.poster.avif?t=1723346766\" width=202 height=152 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147050/extras/4913fa74f6d0ba820e152dc073ba6ce0.webm?t=1723346766\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147050/extras/4913fa74f6d0ba820e152dc073ba6ce0.mp4?t=1723346766\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 可爱猫猫，漫步地城。<br></li><li> 弹墙跳跃，躲避陷阱。<br></li><li> 收集金币，夺取宝石。<br></li><li> 隐藏地图，静候发现<br></li><li> 近百关卡，等你挑战。</li></ul>",
